	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65198929"><p>A wise early-career mentor said time estimates should be double then use the next-highest unit of time.</p><p>1 hour becomes 2 days.<br>1 day becomes 2 weeks.<br>10 minutes becomes 20 hours.<br>And so on.</p><p>Sometimes you get lucky - 10 minutes becomes <b>only</b> 4 hours.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_65198929">

</div>
</div>

