	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65198997">The head of Maintenance for a local school district. When he was asked how much a project would cost, he would make his best estimate double it and add 20%. He said by doing this he would occasionally come out under budget and look like a hero</div>
